{
  "stem": "1511.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't remember exactly what happened later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because I know later on, the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Hitler, without giving a sign, he just-- the Russian were so good with them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They bake bread, and they send wagons of bread to the German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they started a war so suddenly that nobody expected it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you know, and they-- so they start to come in in the other, in the other side too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But still, the Russian were pushing them back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was going on a war between-- they didn't get it the whole thing right away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It took a long time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the meantime, I had no place to go, because the Russian, again, when they were on this side, they took all the people what they own-- they own business and things like that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they send them away, to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But in Russia, you're not allowed to have any business on your own.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Everything belongs to the government, and you work for them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they, whatever they give you, this is-- is enough.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I couldn't be with my uncles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I came back, and I stayed with this young couple, with my cousins.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took him away in the war, and they took the other cousin's husband away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then I found a girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Her name was Baltscha.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were also about seven kids.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The mother died, and her husband-- her father left them, and he went to live with another woman or something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they accepted me to their house.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
